Supported notification destinations:
	•	Email
	•	Microsoft Teams
	•	PagerDuty
	•	Slack
	•	Webhook
	•	Notification triggers available:
	•	Start – when the job begins
	•	Success – when the job completes successfully
	•	Failure – when the job fails (selected in the screenshot)
	•	Duration warning – when job execution exceeds expected time
	•	Streaming backlog – when streaming job backlog increases abnormally
	•	Destination dropdown: You can select where to send notifications (e.g., email, Teams, etc.)
	•	Additional options:
	•	Mute notifications for skipped runs
	•	Mute notifications for canceled runs
	•	Add notification button: Allows adding multiple destinations with different trigger types.
